      <title>美国最高法院驳回币安避免加密货币诉讼的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-supreme-court-rejects-bid-by-oil-companiesshell-toss-honolulus-climate-suit-2025-01-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，美国最高法院驳回了币安及其创始人赵长鹏的诉讼，该诉讼旨在避免投资者对这家全球最大加密货币交易所提起的诉讼，投资者指控该交易所非法出售未注册的代币，这些代币已大幅贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-supreme-court-rejects-bid-by-oil-companiesshell-toss-honolulus-climate-suit-2025-01-13/</guid>
